{"title":"战士诗画","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士诗画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你的干劲大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你的干劲大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见了泰山也不怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你的干劲小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见块砖头也绊倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（杨占兴）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身披绿衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸是麻斑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看麻子多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽又壮观。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我若麻子少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射手脸难看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我若麻子多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人心喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（李风良）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当了解放军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色军装身上穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整齐清洁又合身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩手走路多带劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步行如轻云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房东大娘眯眼笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问我为啥这样兴奋？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因我穿上新军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当上了解放军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（宋仁振、滕建兴）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天冷，北风急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长下岗月儿西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拿针线灯下坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄为我缝棉衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针针线线密密缝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情意缝在我心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（傅维顺）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是我们指导员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已是夜深十二点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人还在宿舍转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨个床铺把被盖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是我们指导员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贾洪太）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不向天求饶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担担往上挑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓢瓢往下浇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民来抗旱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不向天求饶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（艺军）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗一行沟一趟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗一行，沟一趟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清清河水沟里淌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行行有我们的汗珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趟趟有我们的力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠在地里开花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量在地里成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那丰收的麦穗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是对战士的褒奖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（张云海）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家在河南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里来信谈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡种水稻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱地变水田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家提口号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年变江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加油来学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文武要双全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"服役期满还家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取当个好社员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（张士林）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔本栏诗选自驻济南部队的“军人诗歌”；画选自“军人画展”〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}